{"article_id":"fwCcK46sRCo0FcEa","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"( CNN )","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"Donald Trump vowed as a candidate to kill Obamacare in short order .","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"But more than two weeks into his presidency , some Republicans are starting to ask :","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"What happened to repealing the law quickly ?","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"The sentiment is beginning to simmer within the influential conservative wing of the Republican Party","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"and hints at what could be the opening of an intra-party rift","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"as the GOP 's mission","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"to overhaul the country 's health care system","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"appears to be losing steam .","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"In one faction are lawmakers increasingly wary of the pitfalls of a quick and sweeping repeal of the Affordable Care Act .","depth":5},{"id":10,"text":"In recent days , top congressional Republicans","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"who are most intimately involved in health care policy","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"have urged moderation :","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"Fearing the consequences of a rapid repeal ,","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"they have begun to speak of `` repairing '' the law","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"and even preserving aspects of it","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"that are working .","depth":10},{"id":17,"text":"That shift in tone has irked other Republicans","depth":10},{"id":18,"text":"who are eager to take a swift vote","depth":12},{"id":19,"text":"to roll back as much of Obamacare","depth":12},{"id":20,"text":"as possible .","depth":11},{"id":21,"text":"Their fear :","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"their conservative constituents back home wo n't settle for anything else .","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"`` For goodness sake , we should be able to put something on President Trump 's desk","depth":11},{"id":24,"text":"that 's at least as good as what we put on President Obama 's desk .","depth":11},{"id":25,"text":"Not something watered down , ''","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"Rep. Jim Jordan , R-Ohio , told CNN in an interview .","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"`` Let 's repeal it .","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"Let 's do what the voters sent us here","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"to do . ''","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"Asked about the political ramifications","depth":11},{"id":31,"text":"of repealing less than what the House has voted for in the past ,","depth":11},{"id":32,"text":"Jordan responded forcefully .","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"`` That 'd just be the flat out wrong thing","depth":12},{"id":34,"text":"to do .","depth":12},{"id":35,"text":"No .","depth":12},{"id":36,"text":"Just flat out wrong , ''","depth":12},{"id":37,"text":"he said .","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"Even Trump now seems to lower expectations .","depth":6},{"id":39,"text":"In an interview with Fox News ' Bill O'Reilly","depth":12},{"id":40,"text":"that aired before the Super Bowl Sunday ,","depth":12},{"id":41,"text":"Trump referred to the process","depth":13},{"id":42,"text":"of overhauling the health care system","depth":13},{"id":43,"text":"as `` very complicated ''","depth":12},{"id":44,"text":"and would n't commit to a firm timeline","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"on when an Obamacare alternative would be rolled out .","depth":11},{"id":46,"text":"`` I would like to say","depth":12},{"id":47,"text":"by the end of the year at least the rudiments ,","depth":12},{"id":48,"text":"but we should have something within the year and the following year , ''","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"Trump said","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"For the most conservative members of the House , that timeline might be unacceptable .","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"Jordan , a member of the conservative House Freedom Caucus , along with the group 's chairman , Rep. Mark Meadows , released a statement last week","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"calling on House leadership to bring for a vote the Obamacare repeal bill","depth":12},{"id":53,"text":"that the House passed during the last Congress .","depth":12},{"id":54,"text":"( That measure was vetoed by President Barack Obama . )","depth":11},{"id":55,"text":"The 2015 bill would have repealed the mandates","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"that individuals have health coverage","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"and that companies with 50 or more employees provide employees affordable insurance .","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"It also would have stripped away Obamacare 's federal subsidies by 2018 ,","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"eliminated funding for Medicaid expansion","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"and canceled a multitude of taxes .","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"It gave lawmakers two years","depth":6},{"id":62,"text":"to come up with a replacement plan .","depth":6},{"id":63,"text":"House Speaker Paul Ryan and other top Republicans are currently crafting a similar budget reconciliation bill","depth":7},{"id":64,"text":"that would unravel big chunks of the law .","depth":7},{"id":65,"text":"But that process has become complicated by pressure","depth":7},{"id":66,"text":"to include Obamacare replacement measures in that legislation .","depth":7},{"id":67,"text":"Ryan said at a news conference last week","depth":7},{"id":68,"text":"that he now hopes to move Obamacare legislation by the end of March .","depth":7},{"id":69,"text":"Meadows told CNN","depth":8},{"id":70,"text":"that the party needs to move much faster .","depth":8},{"id":71,"text":"`` I do n't know","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"that there 's any new revelations","depth":12},{"id":73,"text":"that are going to come up","depth":12},{"id":74,"text":"by waiting 60 to 90 more days , ''","depth":11},{"id":75,"text":"Meadows said .","depth":9},{"id":76,"text":"`` We 're making the whole idea of repeal and replacement far more complex and laborious","depth":11},{"id":77,"text":"than it needs to be","depth":11},{"id":78,"text":"and I think","depth":11},{"id":79,"text":"it 's time","depth":12},{"id":80,"text":"that we just make some decisions","depth":13},{"id":81,"text":"and move forward with ( the repeal bill ) . ''","depth":13},{"id":82,"text":"On considering anything less than what was voted on in 2015 ,","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"Meadows quipped :","depth":11},{"id":84,"text":"`` You do n't get any credit with any of your constituents","depth":12},{"id":85,"text":"if you do that . ''","depth":12},{"id":86,"text":"It 's not clear how widespread the calls","depth":7},{"id":87,"text":"to vote on the 2015 Obamacare repeal bill","depth":7},{"id":88,"text":"could become .","depth":6},{"id":89,"text":"But","depth":7},{"id":90,"text":"when members of the House Freedom Caucus gather for their weekly dinner in Washington early this week ,","depth":8},{"id":91,"text":"they plan to discuss the topic","depth":9},{"id":92,"text":"and try to garner broader support ,","depth":9},{"id":93,"text":"according to a source .","depth":6},{"id":94,"text":"Meadows and Jordan said","depth":5},{"id":95,"text":"they support voting on a replacement bill at the same time as the repeal legislation ,","depth":6},{"id":96,"text":"and are exploring potential legislation","depth":7},{"id":97,"text":"that they could rally around .","depth":7},{"id":98,"text":"Last week , members of the Freedom Caucus met with Sen. Rand Paul","depth":7},{"id":99,"text":"to discuss the Kentucky Republican 's Obamacare legislation and a potential cross-chamber partnership .","depth":7},{"id":100,"text":"Paul has been adamant","depth":8},{"id":101,"text":"that an Obamacare alternative must be ready","depth":9},{"id":102,"text":"before the GOP votes to repeal the law","depth":9},{"id":103,"text":"-- a priority","depth":8},{"id":104,"text":"echoed by many fellow Republicans .","depth":8},{"id":105,"text":"Reassuring the public","depth":8},{"id":106,"text":"that the GOP wo n't allow millions to suddenly lose coverage","depth":8},{"id":107,"text":"will become an increasingly urgent task ,","depth":7},{"id":108,"text":"as Republican lawmakers start to receive blowback from constituents","depth":7},{"id":109,"text":"for dismantling the Affordable Care Act at town halls across the country .","depth":7},{"id":110,"text":"Doug Heye ,","depth":7},{"id":111,"text":"who served as top aide to former House Majority Leader Eric Cantor ,","depth":7},{"id":112,"text":"scoffed at the complaints","depth":8},{"id":113,"text":"coming from some Republicans","depth":8},{"id":114,"text":"that the party is n't voting to repeal Obamacare quickly enough .","depth":7},{"id":115,"text":"Heye , a CNN political commentator , witnessed first-hand the party 's months-long effort in 2014","depth":9},{"id":116,"text":"to craft an Obamacare replacement bill","depth":9},{"id":117,"text":"-- an exercise","depth":9},{"id":118,"text":"that did n't go anywhere .","depth":9},{"id":119,"text":"`` I can tell you chapter and verse about 2014 and all the meetings","depth":10},{"id":120,"text":"that I went to on replacement","depth":10},{"id":121,"text":"where we never produced draft legislation , ''","depth":9},{"id":122,"text":"Heye said .","depth":8},{"id":123,"text":"`` We could do the repeal vote","depth":8},{"id":124,"text":"-- that was easy .","depth":8},{"id":125,"text":"Then we tried to craft the replacement legislation ,","depth":9},{"id":126,"text":"which","depth":10},{"id":127,"text":"not having the Senate and not having the White House","depth":11},{"id":128,"text":"-- it was still very much of a political act .","depth":11},{"id":129,"text":"And now it 's more than that . ''","depth":8}],"relations":[{"parent":259,"left":0,"right":258,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":258,"left":214,"right":257,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":214,"left":166,"right":213,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":166,"left":137,"right":165,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":137,"left":132,"right":136,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{